      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"heavy weight\" though. it's different. it's like the essence of me is just... evaporated. the artist, the person who actually perceives the world, they're gone. there's nothing left inside the skin. how can anyone care about a person who isn't even there anymore? it's just an empty vessel.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
